    • Method Detail

      • getPlaylists

        Result getPlaylists(String qid,
                    String cookie)
        Get all playlists of user qid in qq music platform.
        Parameters:
        qid - Your qq number.
        cookie - Your cookie for qq music.
        Returns:
        All playlists created by qid, wrapped by Result DTO, the data is PagedDataDTO<QQMusicPlaylist>.
        API Note:
        GET /user/playlist?id=qid

      • getDetailPlaylist

        Result getDetailPlaylist(String tid,
                         String cookie)
        Get detail playlist with tid.
        Parameters:
        tid - The playlist's global tid.
        cookie - Your qq music cookie.
        Returns:
        Detail playlist wrapped by Result DTO, the data is QQMusicDetailPlaylist.
        API Note:
        GET /playlist?id=tid

      • createPlaylist

        Result createPlaylist(String name,
                      String cookie)
        Create playlist.
        Parameters:
        name - The name of playlist.
        cookie - Your cookie for qq music.
        Returns:
        The response of request wrapped by Result DTO.
        API Note:
        GET /playlist/create?name=name

      • deletePlaylist

        Result deletePlaylist(String dirIds,
                      String cookie)
        Delete playlist with dirIds dirIds.
        Parameters:
        dirIds - The dirId of playlist you want to delete, multiple dirId separated with comma.
        cookie - Your cookie for qq music.
        Returns:
        The response of request wrapped by Result DTO.
        API Note:
        GET /playlist/delete?dirid=dirIds

      • addSongsToPlaylist

        Result addSongsToPlaylist(int dirId,
                          String songsMid,
                          String cookie)
        Add songs with mids songsMid to playlist with dirId dirId
        Parameters:
        dirId - The dirId of the playlist.
        songsMid - The mid of songs, multiple mid separated with comma.
        cookie - Your qq music cookie.
        Returns:
        The response of request wrapped by Result DTO.
        API Note:
        GET /playlist/add?dirid=dirId&mid=songsMid

      • moveSongsToOtherPlaylist

        Result moveSongsToOtherPlaylist(String songsId,
                                int fromDirId,
                                int toDirId,
                                String cookie)
        Move songs songsId from playlist with fromDirId to playlist with toDirId.
        Parameters:
        songsId - Songs id to be moved, multiple songs id separated with comma.
        fromDirId - DirId of source playlist.
        toDirId - DirId of target playlist.
        cookie - Your qq music cookie.
        Returns:
        The response of request wrapped by Result DTO.
        API Note:
        GET /move?id=songsId&from_dir=fromDirId&to_dir=toDirId

      • removeSongsFromPlaylist

        Result removeSongsFromPlaylist(int dirId,
                               String songsId,
                               String cookie)
        Remove songs with song id songId from playlist with dirId dirId.
        Parameters:
        dirId - The dirId of playlist that you want to remove songs from.
        songsId - The songs' id, multiple songs id separated with comma.
        cookie - Your qq music cookie.
        Returns:
        The response of request wrapped by Result DTO.
        API Note:
        GET /playlist/remove?dirid=dirId&id=songsId
